tle=\"Johnson &amp; Johnson\">JNJ</a></span>) stock to my portfolio and</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1180491673/image_1180491673.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745229-johnson-and-johnson-dividend-legend-at-a-discount", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 19:00:00"}, {"id": "4745348", "title": "Middlesex Water: This Dividend King Is Not Worth Your Time", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://media.gettyimages.com/id/2160087422/photo/aerial-view-of-two-environmental-engineers-work-at-wastewater-treatment-plants-water.jpg?b=1&amp;s=612x612&amp;w=0&amp;k=20&amp;c=kD3Rdaauuhe82V0P1-w5zO4iXjHFq_YQlAkOYepE0Yg=\" alt=\"Aerial View of Two Environmental engineers work at wastewater treatment plants, Water management concept.\" data-id=\"2160087422\" data-type=\"getty-image\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">BugTiger/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Legendary dividend stock <strong>Middlesex Water</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MSEX\" title=\"Middlesex Water Company\">MSEX</a></span>) has been pummeled in recent weeks. The stock made a new relative high in early November, only to move from $70 to $55 in virtually a straight line. Does that make the</p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745348-middlesex-water-this-dividend-king-is-not-worth-your-time", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 18:56:01"}, {"id": "4745365", "title": "December Fed Takeaway: A Foggier Outlook And A More Cautious Path", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172717098/image_172717098.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"US Federal Reserve, Washington DC (in winter)\" dat