-of-tesla-robotaxi-and-excessive-valuation", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 18:41:55"}, {"id": "4745342", "title": "American Water Works: Time To Buy This Water Utility Now", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1466744580/image_1466744580.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Water running from tap into kitchen sink\" data-id=\"1466744580\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1466744580/image_1466744580.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1466744580/image_1466744580.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1466744580/image_1466744580.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1466744580/image_1466744580.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1466744580/image_1466744580.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1466744580/image_1466744580.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1466744580/image_1466744580.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1466744580/image_1466744580.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\">Tap water running into a kitchen sink.</p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Liudmila Chernetska</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In life and investing, consistency matters greatly. This is because wealth and success rarely come quickly. Even if it did, it's going to take commitment and dedication to maintain and buil